the deck.</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gallery\">\n        \n          <figure>\n            <div class=\"photo-tile\" data-media-id=\"companycam_deborah_justice_checklist_photo\">L</div>\n            <figcaption>Leak detection field documentation from a real Aquatrace workflow</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <figure>\n            <div class=\"photo-tile\" data-media-id=\"companycam_camp_mikell_checklist_photo\">C</div>\n            <figcaption>Commercial pool report evidence organized for owner review</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section warm\">\n      <div class=\"section-heading\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Reviews</p>\n        <h2>Owners hire Aquatrace when they need a clear answer.</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"reviews\">\n        \n          <blockquote>\n            <p>They found what everyone else missed and explained it without making us feel dumb.</p>\n            <cite>Residential pool owner</cite>\n          </blockquote>\n          <blockquote>\n            <p>The report was clear enough for our maintenance team and ownership group.</p>\n            <cite>Commercial property manager</cite>\n          </blockquote>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"badges\" aria-label=\"Field standards\">\n      <span>Pressure testing</span><span>Dye testing</span><span>Underwater documentation</span><span>Photo-backed findings</span><span>Approval-gated follow-up</span>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"section-heading\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Guides</p>\n        <h2>Helpful leak guides before you book.</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"article-list\">\n        \n          <a href=\"/guides/water-loss-vs-evaporation\">\n            <strong>How to tell if pool water loss is more than evaporation</strong>\n            <span>A plain-language guide built from the Aquatrace leak detection workflow.</span>\n          </a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section lead\" id=\"estimate\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Start Here</p>\n        <h2>Tell us what the pool is doing.</h2>\n        <p>Share the city, how much water you are losing, and whether it is a pool, spa, or commercial site. Nexi will park the request for owner review.</p>\n      </div>\n      <form method=\"post\" action=\"/api/sites/aquatrace-m8-receipt-1783450709297/leads\">\n        <label>Name <input name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" required /></label>\n        <label>Email <input name=\"email\" type=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" /></label>\n        <label>Phone <input name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\" /></label>\n        <label>City <input name=\"city\" autocomplete=\"address-level2\" /></label>\n        <label>What are you seeing? <textarea name=\"message\" required></textarea></label>\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"consent.email\" value=\"true\" />\n        <button type=\"submit\">Request leak help</button>\n      </form>\n    </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <strong>Aquatrace Swimming Pool Leak Detection</strong><br />\n      Internal NexTeam staging build. Custom domain and SSL are pending owner Cloudflare setup.\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>",
